{"tid":2001962,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大摩重申領展(00823.HK)「減持」評級 目標價73元","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:10:39.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9102b7764442e8b494737fb795d7138a03bcb360","tid":2001962,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】去年領展（0823）一度挑戰「紅底股」，表現遠勝同業。但摩根士丹利昨日發表報告指出，領展今年將迎來轉捩點，股價將會跑輸其他香港地產股，每基金單位分派（DPU）將放緩，其零售租金收入增長亦會在今年跌穿20%的長期水平（見圖），因此予以「減持」評級。領展昨日跌1.9%，收報76.45元，見52周低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200222/s00064/1b9a7db4fa87657cec255c7de524f6e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200222%2Fs00064%2F1b9a7db4fa87657cec255c7de524f6e2.jpg&h=e1e93f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b9033b6f3031a8f7406ff8309298643954a8401","tid":2001962,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"@日"},{"pid":"028c4deed9734b4706bc89699b1837e6e15a5dd1","tid":2001962,"uid":282634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"好似係燈黎"},{"pid":"083b1638989a9603a58a4132f29952540fa10a78","tid":2001962,"uid":357807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"Reit 黎講， 778真係屌打823"},{"pid":"f6984a8423d3c3efae35111cbadb918fce788fb1","tid":2001962,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"又跌啦"},{"pid":"3b97669f39662f26b9b214a7cb68ca913b48b7c7","tid":2001962,"uid":352734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}